<%= javascript_include_tag('clipboard.js') %>
<%= javascript_include_tag('tolkien_api.js') %>
<%= javascript_include_tag('dropdown.js') %>

<p style="color: green"><%= notice %></p>
<body>
  <main>

    <h1>The Lord of the Quotes</h1>

    <h1>What has Middle Earth been saying? </h1>



    <div class="main-ring">
      <div class="container">
      <img id="image" class="rotate2" src="<%= asset_path("ring2.png") %>" >
        <div class="bottom-left">Bottom Left placeholder </div>
        <div class="top-left">Choose quotes by character:
          <form>
            <select>
              <option disabled hidden selected>Select</option>
              <option value="Aragorn">Aragorn</option>
              <option value="Bilbo">Bilbo</option> 
              <option value="Boromir">Boromir</option>
              <option value="Celeborn">Celeborn</option>
              <option value="Elrond">Elrond</option>
            </select>
              <button type="button" class="fetch-specific-quote" >Fetch a Quote!</button>
          </form>
        </div>
        <div class="top-right quoteByAuthor"> <%= @tolkien_character["text"] %> ~ <%= @tolkien_character["character"] %> </div>
        <div class="bottom-right">Current Weather in<br> <strong>Middle Earth</strong>, Maryland: <br>
          <%= @weather['weather'][0]['description'].titlecase %> <br> <%= @weather['main']['temp'] %> &#8451
        </div>
        <div class="centered"> <span id="tolkien" class="quote"> <%= @tolkien['text'] %> ~ <%= @tolkien['character'] %> </span>
        <button class="btn-clipboard" onclick="copyToClipboard()" data-original-title="Copy to clipboard">Copy</button>
          <div class="generate-button-div"> 
          <button class="generate-button"> Random Quote! </button>
          <a href="#" data-quote-id=<%= @tolkien['id'] %> class="favorite"> Favorite </a>
          <a href="#" class="unFavorite"> Un Favorite </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div> 
    </div>
    <br>

    <div class="container">
          <div class="ticker">
            <div class="title"><h5>Breaking News</h5></div>
            <div class="news">
              <marquee>
                <p>
                  Entwives reportedly sighted on the west bank of a southern bow of the river Carnen, flowing into the Sea of Rh√ªn /// Hobbit's take Gold Medal in Curling at Middle Earth Winter Olympics, coach attributes success to, "being low to the ground" /// Exclusive interview with the Balrog tonight at 9pm, "I'm just misunderstood." /// Minas Tirith FC win the Champion's League final 3-2 against Isengard, with only three player fatalities /// The Rohan Derby mired in controversy after Elvish team ~ Valaya's Breath ~ accused of using magic to win /// The Epic Dwarven Brewery Tour now open for tickets, get yours online now /// Farmers in the Westfold grow a 2708lb pumpkin, beating the famed Farmer Maggot's Guiness Book of ME Records entry of 3025 /// Goblin factory workers unionize, spokesman releases statement, "Nah dis is fair, innit" /// The Nazghul Nine Ballet House announce Middle Earth tour and tickets sell out immediately /// Weathertop Restoration Fund reaches it's crowdfunding target after mysterious benefactor donates a set of mithril armour /// Cave Troll sanctuary in the Misty Mountains set to open summer this year /// The final Palantir recovered in a garage sale in Dale, owner say's, "We used it as a paperweight for years." /// Prancing Pony celebrates its 50th year of operation with a limited run of themed beer steins - more details to follow /// Results now coming in from Mordor general election, Sauron reported to have 98.5% of the votes ///
                </p>
              </marquee>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
  </main>    
</body>


